rds-winners.html |title=8th Annual Indie Series Awards Winners |publisher=Indie Series Awards |accessdate=April 14, 2017}}</ref> |- | Best Guest Actress (Drama) | Elizabeth Hubbard | {{nom}} | align=center| <ref name="8th Indie"/> |- | Best Ensemble (Drama) | | {{nom}} | align=center| <ref name="8th Indie"/> |- | Best Makeup | Lora Lee | {{nom}} | align=center| <ref name="8th Indie"/> |- |2018 | [[45th Daytime Creative Arts Emmy Awards]] | [[Daytime Emmy Award for Outstanding Guest Performer Actor in a Digital Daytime Drama Series|Outstanding Guest Performer in a Digital Daytime Drama Series]] | [[Jennifer Bassey]] as Beverly Newman | {{nom}} | align=center| <ref name="45th nom"/> |}
